        <svcproc svcproctype="describe" graphiccount="0">
            <title>Dana Spicer Heavy Axle and Brake Division Information Sheet</title>
            <para>P/N: 129855</para>
            <para>
                <title>15040S Ring Gear Nut and Bolt Kit - Service</title>
            </para>
            <para>This service kit contains replacement ring gear bolts; washers and nuts that can be used in place of
                standard production parts in 15040S axles. For vehicles utilizing the 15040S axle in primarily off-hwy
                applications, the addition of the thru-hardened washer at the ring gear bolted joint increases the clamp
                load substantially. With the addition of the washer it is also necessary to use a longer ring gear bolt.
                If replacing standard parts with the enclosed replacement parts make sure to change out all 16 bolts and
                nuts with the enclosed parts, do not mix parts up.
            </para>
            <specpara>
                <important>
                    <para>Due to a stack up clearance within the 15040S axle in 7.17 ratio axles only, the parts in this
                        kit will not work in those ratios. You must use the original replacement parts designed for that
                        ratio axle.
                    </para>
                </important>
            </specpara>
